divs: Sighting DetailsMe and a friend were travelling near "three corners" (from Ninevah to L-burg, and as soon as we got at three corners we seen in the direction of town (L-burg) two oval, egg-shaped glow in the dark, not shining, objects in the sky. As soon as we seen them they took off one after the other right over the horizon very very very fast. The whole thing lasted 5 seconds or less. Friend was just as excited as me as to what we had seen. Not a very good report I know but it wasnt a reflection in glass, we had windows rolled down... We dont know what they were, skies were clear.

Summary: Two objects moving very fast together over a night time horizon...
